<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Design Gallery · Daily Brief #{{ issue_number }}</title>
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body {
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Display",
               "Pretendard", "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
  background: #0b0a08;
  color: #f5f4ef;
  line-height: 1.55;
  min-height: 100vh;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}
a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

.container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }

.hero {
  text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
}
.hero .super {
  display: inline-block; padding: 0.3rem 0.9rem;
  background: rgba(245,158,11,0.15); color: #fcd34d;
  border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.4); border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.hero h1 {
  font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.6rem); font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
}
.hero .sub {
  font-size: 1.05rem; opacity: 0.75; max-width: 56ch; margin: 0 auto;
}
.hero .meta {
  margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem; opacity: 0.55;
}

.grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.3rem;
}

.card {
  border-radius: 18px; overflow: hidden; position: relative;
  display: block; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  min-height: 300px;
  color: #fff;
}
.card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); }

.card .preview {
  height: 180px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-weight: 900; font-size: 2.5rem;
}
.card .body { padding: 1.2rem 1.4rem 1.4rem; background: #17150f; }
.card .eyebrow {
  font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: #fcd34d; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.card h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
.card p { font-size: 0.88rem; opacity: 0.72; margin: 0; }
.card .arrow {
  display: inline-block; margin-top: 0.8rem;
  font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fcd34d;
}

/* 카드 프리뷰 배경 (각 스타일의 분위기) */
.preview-magazine {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #f59e0b 100%);
  color: #1d1d1f;
}
.preview-magazine::after {
  content: "Aa"; font-family: "SF Pro Display", sans-serif; font-weight: 900;
}
.preview-newspaper {
  background: #f5f0e6; color: #17110a;
  font-family: "Playfair Display", Georgia, serif;
}
.preview-newspaper::after { content: "The Brief"; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
.preview-brevity {
  background: #faf9f7; color: #ff6b00;
}
.preview-brevity::after {
  content: "▪▪▪"; font-size: 3rem; letter-spacing: 0.3em;
}
.preview-terminal {
  background: #0a0a0a; color: #00ff88;
  font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
}
.preview-terminal::after {
  content: "> _"; font-size: 2rem;
  animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
}
@keyframes blink { 0%, 50% { opacity: 1; } 51%, 100% { opacity: 0.2; } }
.preview-reels {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ef4444 0%, #8b5cf6 50%, #06b6d4 100%);
  color: #fff; font-size: 2rem;
}
.preview-reels::after { content: "▶"; font-size: 3.5rem; }

.current-link {
  margin-top: 3rem; padding: 1.3rem 1.5rem;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 14px;
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem;
}
.current-link .label { font-size: 0.85rem; opacity: 0.65; }
.current-link .value { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-top: 0.2rem; }
.current-link a {
  padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem; background: #fcd34d; color: #1d1d1f;
  border-radius: 999px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.85rem;
}

footer {
  text-align: center; padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
  color: rgba(245,244,239,0.5); font-size: 0.82rem;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="super">Design Gallery</div>
    <h1>같은 뉴스, 5가지 분위기</h1>
    <p class="sub">오늘자 Daily Brief 데이터를 그대로 써서 완전히 다른 UI 5종을 만들었습니다. 하나씩 눌러보세요.</p>
    <div class="meta">Issue #{{ issue_number }} · {{ period_label }} · {{ generation_timestamp }}</div>
  </header>

  <div class="grid">
    <a class="card" href="./magazine.html">
      <div class="preview preview-magazine"></div>
      <div class="body">
        <div class="eyebrow">Variant A</div>
        <h3>Magazine</h3>
        <p>Apple News 풍의 라이트 매거진. 히어로 + 카드 그리드, 둥근 모서리, 여백이 넓은 고급감.</p>
        <div class="arrow">열기 →</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="./newspaper.html">
      <div class="preview preview-newspaper"></div>
      <div class="body">
        <div class="eyebrow">Variant B</div>
        <h3>Newspaper</h3>
        <p>New York Times 풍의 고전 신문 레이아웃. Serif 폰트, 3단 컬럼, 드롭캡으로 진중함.</p>
        <div class="arrow">열기 →</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="./brevity.html">
      <div class="preview preview-brevity"></div>
      <div class="body">
        <div class="eyebrow">Variant C</div>
        <h3>Smart Brevity</h3>
        <p>Axios·Morning Brew 풍의 초단문 브리핑. "Why it matters" 박스, 강한 오렌지 포인트.</p>
        <div class="arrow">열기 →</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="./terminal.html">
      <div class="preview preview-terminal"></div>
      <div class="body">
        <div class="eyebrow">Variant D</div>
        <h3>Terminal</h3>
        <p>Bloomberg 터미널 풍의 다크 모노스페이스. 데이터 테이블, 티커, 블링크 커서.</p>
        <div class="arrow">열기 →</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="./reels.html">
      <div class="preview preview-reels"></div>
      <div class="body">
        <div class="eyebrow">Variant E</div>
        <h3>Reels</h3>
        <p>TikTok / Stories 풍의 풀스크린 수직 스와이프. 기사당 한 화면, 그라디언트 배경.</p>
        <div class="arrow">열기 →</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="../index.html" style="background: #1a1915;">
      <div class="preview" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1915 0%, #3b2d1a 100%);">
        <div style="font-size: 1rem; text-align: center; padding: 1rem;">
          Current Production<br>
          <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; opacity: 0.6; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;">Dark Amber</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        <div class="eyebrow">Current (Live)</div>
        <h3>Dark Amber Minimal</h3>
        <p>현재 실제 배포 중인 다크 미니멀 브리핑. 기존 디자인과 비교해 보세요.</p>
        <div class="arrow">열기 →</div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="current-link">
    <div>
      <div class="label">같은 데이터로 렌더링됨</div>
      <div class="value">Issue #{{ issue_number }} · {{ all_count }}개 기사 · must_know {{ must_know|length }}건</div>
    </div>
    <a href="../index.html">현재 프로덕션 보기</a>
  </div>
</div>

<footer>
  Daily Brief Design Gallery · {{ generation_timestamp }}
</footer>

</body>
</html>
